title: charityfashionshow.org (Charity Fashion Show) is coming to NYC!
desc: Karlie Kloss, Vogue covergirl and runway superstar, was discovered at a charity fashion show in a mall in St. Louis, Missouri. She was only 13. It's Your Turn! charityfashionshow.org  is planning a legitimate runway event in New York!  SMS CHARITYFASHIONSHOW to 50500 to get contact information.
